{
  "video_id": "JsC9ZHi79jo",
  "title": "How to triple your memory by using this trick | Ricardo Lieuw On | TEDxHaarlem",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Queenie Lee Reviewer: Tanya Cushman"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14880.0,
      "end_time": 17430.0,
      "text": "So, I have a little test for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17990.0,
      "end_time": 19990.0,
      "text": "Don't panic."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19100.0,
      "end_time": 21111.0,
      "text": "I'm not here to judge you."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21111.0,
      "end_time": 23182.0,
      "text": "It's just a little test, OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23412.0,
      "end_time": 28570.0,
      "text": "First, you get 30 seconds to memorize 10 words in the right order."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29271.0,
      "end_time": 34226.0,
      "text": "After that, you get 30 seconds to write down what you remembered."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34246.0,
      "end_time": 38137.0,
      "text": "And then finally, you get 30 seconds to check your answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38537.0,
      "end_time": 40106.0,
      "text": "So, are you guys ready?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40746.0,
      "end_time": 42578.0,
      "text": "Well, we're going to start anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43982.0,
      "end_time": 44982.0,
      "text": "So,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45487.0,
      "end_time": 49207.0,
      "text": "memorize 10 words in the right order in 30 seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49207.0,
      "end_time": 52947.0,
      "text": "in three, two, one, go!"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 82166.0,
      "end_time": 83377.0,
      "text": "OK. Stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 84470.0,
      "end_time": 86715.0,
      "text": "Now write down what you remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 118705.0,
      "end_time": 120120.0,
      "text": "OK, and stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 120912.0,
      "end_time": 123532.0,
      "text": "Now quickly check your answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 144340.0,
      "end_time": 146190.0,
      "text": "OK, and stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 152370.0,
      "end_time": 155104.0,
      "text": "Very exciting; I heard a lot of grunting and moaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 155104.0,
      "end_time": 157483.0,
      "text": "So I hope I didn't stress you out too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 159254.0,
      "end_time": 161825.0,
      "text": "Now a moment of reflection."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 162705.0,
      "end_time": 164565.0,
      "text": "I'd like you to ask yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 166545.0,
      "end_time": 170975.0,
      "text": "\"How did I memorize this, and was it the best way to do it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 176185.0,
      "end_time": 180115.0,
      "text": "Now, for the generation of my parents and grandparents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 180115.0,
      "end_time": 184667.0,
      "text": "being able to memorize something like this was an absolutely essential skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 184677.0,
      "end_time": 188620.0,
      "text": "But nowadays, why would anyone want to remember a list of anything?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 188621.0,
      "end_time": 191602.0,
      "text": "You just take a picture of the screen, and you're done, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 196162.0,
      "end_time": 199143.0,
      "text": "it seemed as if memorizing has somehow become less important."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 199773.0,
      "end_time": 202363.0,
      "text": "So why should we then, in today's day and age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 202363.0,
      "end_time": 204473.0,
      "text": "still want to get better at memorizing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 205274.0,
      "end_time": 208664.0,
      "text": "Well, to answer that question, I'd like to tell you a little story."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 209870.0,
      "end_time": 214367.0,
      "text": "In high school, I flunked a grade, twice."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 214556.0,
      "end_time": 218928.0,
      "text": "After seven years of torture, I finally got my diploma."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 219337.0,
      "end_time": 221268.0,
      "text": "Sweet, sweet freedom!"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 222139.0,
      "end_time": 223473.0,
      "text": "What would I do with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 223853.0,
      "end_time": 224954.0,
      "text": "I didn't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 225333.0,
      "end_time": 226794.0,
      "text": "One thing I did know, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 226794.0,
      "end_time": 229203.0,
      "text": "was that I didn't want to go back to school"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 229553.0,
      "end_time": 231774.0,
      "text": "because that old learning business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 232364.0,
      "end_time": 233854.0,
      "text": "it wasn't cut out for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 234523.0,
      "end_time": 239464.0,
      "text": "So instead, I went to sunny California for nine months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 239464.0,
      "end_time": 242965.0,
      "text": "and there I worked as a bagger, not beggar - bagger."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 243385.0,
      "end_time": 244674.0,
      "text": "So in a supermarket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 244675.0,
      "end_time": 248496.0,
      "text": "I had to put people's groceries in bags, and then I'd get a little tip."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 250685.0,
      "end_time": 254950.0,
      "text": "Surprisingly, that year I learned so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 254385.0,
      "end_time": 257461.0,
      "text": "I learned how to bag a bunch of groceries really, really quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 258560.0,
      "end_time": 260520.0,
      "text": "I learned how to drive a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 260521.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261701.00000000003,
      "text": "And in California,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 261701.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264892.0,
      "text": "people are a little bit more open than they are in Amsterdam."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 264892.0,
      "end_time": 268161.0,
      "text": "So I also learned how to have a little chat with a stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 268161.0,
      "end_time": 269512.0,
      "text": "just for the hell of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 270122.0,
      "end_time": 273930.0,
      "text": "That year I discovered that I don't hate learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 273693.0,
      "end_time": 275953.0,
      "text": "just the specific way of doing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 276513.0,
      "end_time": 279433.0,
      "text": "So I decided to go and study psychology."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 279433.0,
      "end_time": 281262.0,
      "text": "Now for the first time ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 281262.0,
      "end_time": 284469.0,
      "text": "I was getting information that I absolutely wanted to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 284789.0,
      "end_time": 287258.0,
      "text": "Now I was spending more time in the library"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 287258.0,
      "end_time": 291558.0,
      "text": "than I spent skipping school as a teenager, voluntarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 292718.0,
      "end_time": 297310.0,
      "text": "The only problem was that I was spending all of my time in the library"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 297310.0,
      "end_time": 299430.0,
      "text": "because I'd never learned how to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 299830.0,
      "end_time": 304179.0,
      "text": "So I started experimenting with different methods of reading texts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 304179.0,
      "end_time": 305580.0,
      "text": "of memorizing texts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 305580.0,
      "end_time": 309599.0,
      "text": "and I got my reading time of three hours per chapter down to one."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 310599.0,
      "end_time": 315361.0,
      "text": "This way of studying enabled me to do an honors program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 315362.0,
      "end_time": 316975.0,
      "text": "to get my degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 317166.0,
      "end_time": 319500.0,
      "text": "and to fall in love with learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 319666.0,
      "end_time": 323656.0,
      "text": "And now I happily work for a company called Remind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 324650.0,
      "end_time": 327516.0,
      "text": "in which we teach people the science and art of learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 328217.0,
      "end_time": 332670.0,
      "text": "We're trying to bring back into education what we ourselves missed."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 332737.0,
      "end_time": 334116.0,
      "text": "Now for the past three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 334116.0,
      "end_time": 337376.0,
      "text": "we've also organized the Dutch National Memory Championships"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 337376.0,
      "end_time": 338957.0,
      "text": "for high schoolers."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 339407.0,
      "end_time": 343700.0,
      "text": "We do this to show that everybody is capable of amazing feats of memory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 344192.0,
      "end_time": 346972.0,
      "text": "but also to show that memorization"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 347261.0,
      "end_time": 352102.0,
      "text": "is about a lot more than just learning your French or your Spanish words."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 352122.0,
      "end_time": 354603.0,
      "text": "And today I'd also like to share this with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 355202.0,
      "end_time": 357442.0,
      "text": "So, in the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 357563.0,
      "end_time": 359503.0,
      "text": "I made you do this little test,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 360930.0,
      "end_time": 363782.0,
      "text": "just to make you aware of how you're memorizing things right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 364593.0,
      "end_time": 367704.0,
      "text": "Next, I'd like to give you a new type of memory experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 368304.0,
      "end_time": 371920.0,
      "text": "This time you can even sit back and relax."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 371714.0,
      "end_time": 375103.0,
      "text": "So I'm going to ask you to find a comfortable position to sit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 376850.0,
      "end_time": 380991.0,
      "text": "to close your eyes, and to take a deep breath."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 384440.0,
      "end_time": 389991.0,
      "text": "Now, I want you to think of someone you know called John,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 391701.0,
      "end_time": 393501.0,
      "text": "and I want you to see him."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 394672.0,
      "end_time": 399132.0,
      "text": "Now, John just grabbed the sun out of the sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 399132.0,
      "end_time": 401112.0,
      "text": "and he just threw it on your feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 401482.0,
      "end_time": 405370.0,
      "text": "And now your feet are getting really big and red and swollen"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 405370.0,
      "end_time": 409560.0,
      "text": "because John just threw the sun on your feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 410666.0,
      "end_time": 413256.0,
      "text": "Now you look to your knees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 414860.0,
      "end_time": 418488.0,
      "text": "and on your knees, you see 10 little guys playing basketball -"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 418797.0,
      "end_time": 420247.0,
      "text": "very strange sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 420247.0,
      "end_time": 422470.0,
      "text": "And on their shirts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 422470.0,
      "end_time": 426728.0,
      "text": "you can see in brightly colored letters the \"New York Knicks,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 427858.0,
      "end_time": 430288.0,
      "text": "so you have some Knicks on your knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 431467.0,
      "end_time": 436817.0,
      "text": "Next, you look to where your thighs are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 437140.0,
      "end_time": 438534.0,
      "text": "but they're gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 439540.0,
      "end_time": 442123.0,
      "text": "Your thighs have been replaced with Fords, the cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 443240.0,
      "end_time": 445744.0,
      "text": "They could be Ford Focuses or Ford Mustangs."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 446945.0,
      "end_time": 449164.0,
      "text": "Your thighs have been replaced with Fords."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 450126.0,
      "end_time": 452650.0,
      "text": "Now, with your bottom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 452650.0,
      "end_time": 457246.0,
      "text": "you feel a hard plastic seat of a go-kart vibrating."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 458565.0,
      "end_time": 462386.0,
      "text": "With your bottom, you feel the hard plastic seat of a go-kart."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 463621.0,
      "end_time": 467132.0,
      "text": "Your belly starts rumbling very loudly."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 467711.0,
      "end_time": 471710.0,
      "text": "So you follow your belly, and it leads you to McDonald's,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 472292.0,
      "end_time": 477371.0,
      "text": "and there Ronald McDonald starts shooting rays of light at you"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 477371.0,
      "end_time": 478952.0,
      "text": "with a ray gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 480820.0,
      "end_time": 483732.0,
      "text": "Ronald McDonald is shooting rays of light at you with a ray gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 485220.0,
      "end_time": 488161.0,
      "text": "He hits you on your chest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 488161.0,
      "end_time": 493573.0,
      "text": "and now from your chest, a big bush of gray hairs is growing."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 494722.0,
      "end_time": 497597.0,
      "text": "A huge bush of gray hair is growing from your chest."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 498490.0,
      "end_time": 500909.0,
      "text": "So obviously, you hurry home to shave it off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 501453.0,
      "end_time": 504688.0,
      "text": "and on your doormat, you see a letter."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 505550.0,
      "end_time": 509580.0,
      "text": "So you open it and it has good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 510500.0,
      "end_time": 514109.0,
      "text": "As you read it, you feel a huge weight falling off your shoulders."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 514729.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516820.00000000006,
      "text": "A huge weight falling off your shoulders."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 516820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520751.00000000006,
      "text": "Your shoulders get all light and tingly because you just paid all of your bills."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 521111.0,
      "end_time": 522751.0,
      "text": "Big bills, little bills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 522751.0,
      "end_time": 526985.0,
      "text": "each and every bill has been paid for, and you have plenty of money to spare."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 530485.0,
      "end_time": 533137.0,
      "text": "Now you proceed to the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 533137.0,
      "end_time": 535256.0,
      "text": "because now on your neck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 535256.0,
      "end_time": 539533.0,
      "text": "a bunch of tiny bushes of thin blonde hairs have appeared."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 540600.0,
      "end_time": 543895.0,
      "text": "On your neck, a bunch of tiny bushes of thin blonde hair."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 545566.0,
      "end_time": 547427.0,
      "text": "As you look in the mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 547467.0,
      "end_time": 550997.0,
      "text": "suddenly your mouth just starts talking all by itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 551957.0,
      "end_time": 557573.0,
      "text": "and it's saying, \"Yes, we can; yes we can; yes we can.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 559533.0,
      "end_time": 563444.0,
      "text": "Now you turn around, and now suddenly your eyes are, ah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 563732.0,
      "end_time": 567424.0,
      "text": "because Donald Duck just poked out both of your eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 567424.0,
      "end_time": 569893.0,
      "text": "with a trumpet made of pure gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 572524.0,
      "end_time": 576995.0,
      "text": "Now you can open your eyes again and come back to this place."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 576995.0,
      "end_time": 580750.0,
      "text": "Luckily, it's a lot safer here than where you just came from."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 581724.0,
      "end_time": 586149.0,
      "text": "So, I just made you guys memorize"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 586149.0,
      "end_time": 589254.0,
      "text": "the past 10 presidents of the United States of America"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 589254.0,
      "end_time": 590910.0,
      "text": "in the right order."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 592159.0,
      "end_time": 593420.0,
      "text": "Now I'm going to show you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 593421.0,
      "end_time": 595980.0,
      "text": "and then you can see how many of these you still know."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 595980.0,
      "end_time": 599290.0,
      "text": "So with each body part, I'm going to ask you what happened there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 599290.0,
      "end_time": 600510.0,
      "text": "and then you could think of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 600510.0,
      "end_time": 603200.0,
      "text": "Even better would be if you just shout it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 603200.0,
      "end_time": 606201.0,
      "text": "Now, what happened to your feet?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 607441.0,
      "end_time": 610775.0,
      "text": "John threw the sun, yeah - President Johnson."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 610775.0,
      "end_time": 611985.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 618867.0,
      "text": "Now, what happened on your knees? Knicks, yes - President Nixon."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 619618.0,
      "end_time": 622637.0,
      "text": "OK. So what were your thighs replaced with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 623228.0,
      "end_time": 625580.0,
      "text": "Fords - President Ford."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 625580.0,
      "end_time": 628269.0,
      "text": "OK, and what did you feel with your bottom?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 629418.0,
      "end_time": 632490.0,
      "text": "OK, President Carter, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 632129.0,
      "end_time": 634178.0,
      "text": "Some people are ahead of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 635708.0,
      "end_time": 638938.0,
      "text": "Now, your belly led you to McDonald's;"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 638938.0,
      "end_time": 640478.0,
      "text": "what happened?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 641479.0,
      "end_time": 644710.0,
      "text": "OK. Ronald McDonald shooting rays of …"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 644710.0,
      "end_time": 646663.0,
      "text": "So Ronald Reagan."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 646993.0,
      "end_time": 649173.0,
      "text": "He hits in your chest, and you got what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 650540.0,
      "end_time": 652824.0,
      "text": "Big bush of gray hairs - Bush senior."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 652824.0,
      "end_time": 655304.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 658825.0,
      "end_time": 661240.0,
      "text": "Now, your shoulders got light, why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 661914.0,
      "end_time": 664184.0,
      "text": "Paid all your bills - Bill Clinton."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 665449.0,
      "end_time": 668265.0,
      "text": "Now, what did you have on your neck?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 669975.0,
      "end_time": 672796.0,
      "text": "OK, a bush of thin blonde hairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 673356.0,
      "end_time": 674566.0,
      "text": "Bush junior."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 675206.0,
      "end_time": 677212.0,
      "text": "What was your mouth saying?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 678411.0,
      "end_time": 680330.0,
      "text": "\"Yes we can\" - President Obama."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 680331.0,
      "end_time": 682791.0,
      "text": "And what happened to your eyes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 684691.0,
      "end_time": 687947.0,
      "text": "Yeah, Donald Duck, trumpet, pure gold."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 687947.0,
      "end_time": 690230.0,
      "text": "Who else but Donald Trump?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 690713.0,
      "end_time": 696463.0,
      "text": "So, if you memorized more this time than the first time, please stand up."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 703117.0,
      "end_time": 705159.0,
      "text": "OK. So we have almost everyone standing up;"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 705159.0,
      "end_time": 706457.0,
      "text": "that's awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 706667.0,
      "end_time": 711859.0,
      "text": "Now, if you think this way of memorizing is more fun than the last way you used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 711859.0,
      "end_time": 715289.0,
      "text": "please stand up or remain standing if you're already standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 717489.0,
      "end_time": 719539.0,
      "text": "Oh whoa, now we almost have everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 719539.0,
      "end_time": 721150.0,
      "text": "I'm very pleased to see this."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 721150.0,
      "end_time": 722789.0,
      "text": "OK. You guys can sit back down."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 722789.0,
      "end_time": 724780.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 728120.0,
      "end_time": 732870.0,
      "text": "Now, when you make bizarre images to memorize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 732870.0,
      "end_time": 734810.0,
      "text": "suddenly it becomes a lot easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 735130.0,
      "end_time": 738235.0,
      "text": "If you tie these bizarre images to a place you know well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 738235.0,
      "end_time": 739597.0,
      "text": "like your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 739597.0,
      "end_time": 742886.0,
      "text": "suddenly memorizing things in order becomes a lot easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 743700.0,
      "end_time": 744256.0,
      "text": "OK. Well, cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 744256.0,
      "end_time": 746847.0,
      "text": "But I asked you guys in the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 747707.0,
      "end_time": 750370.0,
      "text": "\"Why should we, in today's day and age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 750370.0,
      "end_time": 752887.0,
      "text": "still want to get better at this - at memorizing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 753367.0,
      "end_time": 757536.0,
      "text": "Well, because by getting better in a skill like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 758770.0,
      "end_time": 760838.0,
      "text": "you can also get better at a different skill:"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 760838.0,
      "end_time": 762932.0,
      "text": "the skill of experimentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 763432.0,
      "end_time": 766872.0,
      "text": "By experimenting with different methods of doing things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 767172.0,
      "end_time": 769604.0,
      "text": "I found out that I can get better at anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 770640.0,
      "end_time": 772592.0,
      "text": "I found out what works for me and what doesn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 772982.0,
      "end_time": 775683.0,
      "text": "What if I'd never learned the skill of experimentation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 776630.0,
      "end_time": 778233.0,
      "text": "I may have never gone back to school;"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 778233.0,
      "end_time": 781274.0,
      "text": "I may have never enjoyed studying psychology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 781274.0,
      "end_time": 784240.0,
      "text": "and I probably would not have been standing here today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 784324.0,
      "end_time": 789140.0,
      "text": "because one of the things I thought I really couldn't do was public speaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 790640.0,
      "end_time": 795740.0,
      "text": "Now, there are people of every generation not doing things that they might love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 795740.0,
      "end_time": 797231.0,
      "text": "that they might even be great at"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 797471.0,
      "end_time": 799551.0,
      "text": "because they think they can't do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 800141.0,
      "end_time": 801871.0,
      "text": "So how beautiful would it be"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 801871.0,
      "end_time": 806221.0,
      "text": "if in schools we can teach kids that they can get better at anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 806221.0,
      "end_time": 809670.0,
      "text": "and they can even get better at getting better at things, get it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 810981.0,
      "end_time": 812232.0,
      "text": "But not just the kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 812232.0,
      "end_time": 815540.0,
      "text": "because the older generation is often seen as too old to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 815541.0,
      "end_time": 817452.0,
      "text": "But they're not too rusty."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 817452.0,
      "end_time": 820281.0,
      "text": "Anyone can improve themselves by experimenting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 820281.0,
      "end_time": 822550.0,
      "text": "and I hope you experienced that today."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 823226.0,
      "end_time": 824676.0,
      "text": "Now at Remind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 824676.0,
      "end_time": 828256.0,
      "text": "we break up this process of experimentation into three steps:"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 828676.0,
      "end_time": 832456.0,
      "text": "the check, the experience and the experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 833522.0,
      "end_time": 837270.0,
      "text": "The check is all about becoming aware of what you're doing right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 837827.0,
      "end_time": 841227.0,
      "text": "So maybe during the first test, you became aware of the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 841227.0,
      "end_time": 843353.0,
      "text": "that you just repeat the words over and over"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 843353.0,
      "end_time": 845478.0,
      "text": "and that that doesn't work too well."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 846198.0,
      "end_time": 847367.0,
      "text": "The second step:"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 847368.0,
      "end_time": 852288.0,
      "text": "the experience is all about being open to new possibilities and trying them out."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 852969.0,
      "end_time": 854888.0,
      "text": "So maybe during the visualization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 854888.0,
      "end_time": 858214.0,
      "text": "you realize that this works a bit better or at least you like it more."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 859555.0,
      "end_time": 862940.0,
      "text": "And the third step is the experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 862950.0,
      "end_time": 866115.0,
      "text": "This is about taking something from that new experience that you had"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 866115.0,
      "end_time": 869567.0,
      "text": "and applying it in your own life to see how it works for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 869957.0,
      "end_time": 872185.0,
      "text": "So, maybe you're one of those people"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 872185.0,
      "end_time": 874415.0,
      "text": "that when someone introduces themselves to you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 874416.0,
      "end_time": 876517.0,
      "text": "you just immediately forget their name."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 876517.0,
      "end_time": 877986.0,
      "text": "Yeah, sound familiar?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 877986.0,
      "end_time": 881968.0,
      "text": "And you want to use visualization to do something about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 882318.0,
      "end_time": 886201.0,
      "text": "So far I've only taken you guys through the first two steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 886670.0,
      "end_time": 888492.0,
      "text": "The final step is up to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 888961.0,
      "end_time": 892181.0,
      "text": "So when I'm done here, I'd like you to take a moment for yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 892181.0,
      "end_time": 895542.0,
      "text": "and to write down an experiment on the little card we've given you"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 895542.0,
      "end_time": 898123.0,
      "text": "and to put that in your wallet as a reminder."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 898853.0,
      "end_time": 903510.0,
      "text": "By continually following these steps of experimentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 903520.0,
      "end_time": 904822.0,
      "text": "you discover what you're doing;"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 904822.0,
      "end_time": 907142.0,
      "text": "you keep yourself open to new possibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 907142.0,
      "end_time": 910504.0,
      "text": "and you allow yourself to continually transform."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 910504.0,
      "end_time": 912364.0,
      "text": "And regardless of what you're learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 912364.0,
      "end_time": 915430.0,
      "text": "be it memorizing or martial arts or mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 915543.0,
      "end_time": 918939.0,
      "text": "you'll get better not only in the skill that you're trying to develop,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 918939.0,
      "end_time": 921709.0,
      "text": "but you'll get better at the process of learning itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 922769.0,
      "end_time": 924730.0,
      "text": "And that's something that sticks."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 924730.0,
      "end_time": 928900.0,
      "text": "It's something you could take with you to your new job, your new hobby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 928900.0,
      "end_time": 930109.0,
      "text": "your new relationship, your new whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 930579.0,
      "end_time": 933659.0,
      "text": "So this is something absolutely everyone should know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 934900.0,
      "end_time": 936569.0,
      "text": "and I believe we should teach it in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 936569.0,
      "end_time": 940641.0,
      "text": "But let's not just wait for it to be implemented in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 941810.0,
      "end_time": 944725.0,
      "text": "I also believe that the most important change starts with the individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 945540.0,
      "end_time": 946473.0,
      "text": "It starts with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 947650.0,
      "end_time": 949650.0,
      "text": "So, go out there and experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 949650.0,
      "end_time": 950258.0,
      "text": "Learn something new"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 950258.0,
      "end_time": 952875.0,
      "text": "or a new way of approaching something old"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 952875.0,
      "end_time": 957216.0,
      "text": "because there are few skills as valuable as the art of learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 957766.0,
      "end_time": 959450.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 959460.0,
      "end_time": 961767.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}